==English==

===Etymology===
From {{suffix|Biafra|an|lang=en}}. The "skinny" sense is in reference to the images of extremely skinny Biafran refugees from the {{w|Nigerian Civil War}} that appeared plentifully in English-language media in the 1960s and 1970s.

